org.apache.ambari.server.state

Class SingleSignOnInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.state.SingleSignOnInfo

  • public class SingleSignOnInfo
extends Object
    SingleSignOnInfo encapsulates meta information about a service's support for single sign-on (SSO) integration

    The data is expected to be like 

       <sso>
     <supported>true</supported>
     <ssoEnabledTest>
         {
           "equals": [
             "config-type/sso.enabled.property_name",
             "true"
           ]
         }
     </ssoEnabledTest>
   </sso>
